    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014I've babied it since day one! There isn't a single blemish to be found, and it drives like an absolute dream. I'm honestly a little sad to let it go, but it\u2019s ready for a new home where it'll be just as loved. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
