      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar in pristine, showroom condition. Every facet of this automobile, from its flawless exterior finish to its immaculate interior appointments, reflects a history of uncompromising stewardship. Mechanically superior and aesthetically peerless, this vehicle is curated for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
