    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolute showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it\u2019s been garage-kept the whole time. Not a single scratch or dent to be found, and it still has that fresh, new-car smell! It drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m really sad to see it go, but I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Swing by and take a look\u2014I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
