    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2001 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather. This example is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a redline of 8,000 RPM. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels through a variable M-differential lock. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance: the dual-VANOS system has been rebuilt with Beisan components, and the rear subframe has been reinforced with Turner Motorsport plates to ensure structural integrity. The suspension architecture remains precise, featuring refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampers. The exterior retains its original luster with zero evidence of oxidation or panel misalignment, while the cabin maintains its factory-fresh tactile feel. A mechanically synchronized and cosmetically flawless specimen for the purist collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
